{"tid":118521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼樂園收到懷疑炸彈    數百員工緊急疏散","createTime":"2017-02-13T05:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T14:28:07.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61bc19222e6a34f8546fb160c39314a621ad4fad","tid":118521,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170213/large/1486963952_9a89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170213%2Flarge%2F1486963952_9a89.jpg&h=d48df9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園行政大樓郵件中心，員工中午收到一件可疑物品，懷疑是爆炸品，於12時57分報警，並疏散行政大樓全部數百員工，消防接報派出消防車及救護車戒備，警方爆炸品處理課人員亦奉召到場檢查；現時樂園並沒受影響，遊客不須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n香港迪士尼樂園發言人回應指，今日下午約12時30分，香港迪士尼樂園郵件室發現可疑物品，樂園即時報警，並疏散部分員工。由於事件已交由警方處理，樂園不便評論。"},{"pid":"414679ab68c8ab07e3043ecd0a9e64d8fc849bfb","tid":118521,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:50:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53236167a71976a482c1f876f954fdb10dffcd7e","tid":118521,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"神經過敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a4d27634d2dc020347c552c1e0d6ab167b321c","tid":118521,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"咁件野究竟係咩"},{"pid":"37e9d70377ac41325e4712e37d008f7cb2b48d5f","tid":118521,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899ac810c4ff2934340a1349f098fe1167f495ab","tid":118521,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:53:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34440dba74f343a6b4a3